    {
      "instruction": "<p>Whilst everything is cooking, chop your <strong>cherry</strong> <strong>tomatoes</strong> roughly, then keep chopping them together until they resemble a salsa-like consistency</p><p>Add the <strong>chopped tomatoes</strong> to a bowl with your <strong>chilli flakes</strong> (can't handle the heat? Go easy), a pinch of <strong>salt</strong> and a drizzle of <strong>olive oil</strong></p><p>Stir it all together – this is your <strong>salsa</strong></p><p>Peel and grate your <strong>garlic</strong></p>",
